{"tid":1461442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"My HK建制派聲明嚴重關注示威者損害航空樞紐地位","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:14:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1152587943044a334eb3641f95a1ec59cfe7d9","tid":1461442,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"40名建制派立法會議員發表聯署聲明，強烈要求激進暴力份子，停止再製造暴力衝突。<br />\n<br />\n建制派表示，激進暴力分子非法、不負責任破壞行爲，是造成社會動盪、市民不安的主因，呼籲市民理解警方面對的困難，支持警方依法應對，及早恢復社會秩序，重申現階段只有止暴制亂，支持警方依法有效執法，才能盡快恢復社會秩序，還市民和平穩定的生活。<br />\n<br />\n建制派又對有大批示威者，昨午聚集在機場，嚴重阻礙機場運作，表示嚴重關注，認為已嚴重損害香港作為國際和區域航空樞紐的地位，呼籲示威人士不要再作任何危害本港社會和經濟、影響市民和旅客的舉措。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474392-20190813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474392-20190813.htm&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=8051a4dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474392-20190813.htm&h=09c6a4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474392-20190813.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45bdd3d88e6bc084e3e0b4b1a0f56cb4ca29b38f","tid":1461442,"uid":8873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"建制派班撚樣出嚟反對證明方向正確<br />\n<br />\n依家要做多你幾星期"},{"pid":"f512b0f402e4762d8b4bcf1b9f0d7a012a45959f","tid":1461442,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"歡迎保皇派議員唔好齋出聲明<br />\n應該走入機場勸喻示威者"},{"pid":"be0a379c5a144b33481f43b6c245f203bf240e83","tid":1461442,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"揸到個春袋實一實<br />\n港共開始急啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606ece4a8b72eca9f2416ba29fc730c6cbd7eb7e","tid":1461442,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"